 2022-13082022-12-07,  ,  ,  ,  PMO
ActOfficial Residences Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Remuneration and Conditions of Employment of a Member of the Staff at the Prime Minister’s Residence (Lucja Grabowiec)
PrecisOrder fixing the remuneration and conditions of employment of LUCJA GRABOWIEC, a member of the household staff at the Prime Minister’s residence, which salary is within the range of $54,878 to $61,379 per annum, effective October 20, 2022.
